snippet.title: Ironworker Gaming
snippet.description:
I am Ironworker814 and welcome to my Destiny 2 YouTube channel.  Weapon and armor reviews are my bread and butter, but various videos related to D2 will be sprinkled in as well.  I really enjoy the process of shuffling through older exotic weapons and armor to see how they're holding up in the current sandbox, but I always try to jump on any newly released items as well!  I do my best to keep my content on topic and to the point, while providing the viewer as much information as humanly possible in a single video.  

Also, the community that has sprung up around the channel has also been fantastic!  I've always tried to keep the comment section a safe place for people to politely share their thoughts and ideas without running the risk of being harassed or bullied.  While may not catch every derogatory remark, I do my best to because it's something that I just don't tolerate.  If this channel and community sounds like a good fit for you feel free to hit the subscribe button! 😁🍻

snippet.title: iTzu Gaming
snippet.description:
Haaaallo meine Freunde und willkommen auf dem Kanal "iTzu Gaming". Ich bin ein Professioneller Clash of Clans Spieler bei Tribe Gaming. Hier versuche ich euch Tipps und Tricks für Clash of Clans mitzugeben, sodass ihr noch besser werdet und mehr Spaß am Spiel habt. 

Viele kennen mich aus Events von Supercell, wie dem Update Livestream im Dezember 2016, dem CWL Finale im Anfang des Jahres 2017 oder dem neuesten Projekt – der Clash of Clans Weltmeisterschaft, wo wir als Tribe Gaming das erste Team waren, dass sich qualifizieren konnte.

Allgemein, wenn ihr das beste Gameplay auf Youtube sucht für Clash of Clans seid ihr hier genau richtig. Außerdem bekommt ihr hier immer die schnellsten Informationen zu neuen Updates und allen heißen Informationen rund ums Spiel.

Falls ihr weitere Fragen an mich habt oder jegliche Art von Business Anfragen habt, könnt ihr euch gerne an mich wenden unter folgenden Adresse.

- Discord: iTzu #3145

snippet.title: Gaming Indoors
snippet.description:
Hi YouTube, I'm Ali. Welcome to my channel!

As well as playing and reviewing all kinds of  table-top, roleplaying, board, card and dice games, I'll be getting to grips with the underlying mechanics of modern board games, learning to paint and 3d print my own miniatures, investigating what it takes to design and publish a game, discovering the history behind some of favorite handheld console games and generally doing things a grown man should have stopped doing years ago.

Oh .. And I'll probably play some video games too.

Thanks for watching, welcome to Gaming Indoors!
